#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

class doll
{
public:
doll(string newName,string newhealth,string newammo,string newdamage,string newevasion);
doll();
void output();
string getdamage();
string getname();
friend bool equal(doll data1,doll data2);
private:
string name,health,ammo,damage,evasion;
};


int main()
{
doll data[100];
int num=0;
string tmp;
char next='y';
while(next=='y')
{
string n,h,a,d,e="";
cout<<"input data as follow format name,health,ammo,damage,evasion:";
getline(cin,n,',');
getline(cin,h,',');
getline(cin,a,',');
getline(cin,d,',');
getline(cin,e,'\n');
doll tmpdata(n,h,a,d,e);
data[num]=tmpdata;
cout<<"Have next input data(y/n)?";
cin>>next;
getline(cin,tmp,'\n');
num++;
}

for(int i=0;i<num;i++)
{
data[i].output();
}
if (equal(data[0],data[1]))
cout<<data[0].getname()<<" damage is equal to "<<data[1].getname()<<endl;
else
cout<<data[0].getname()<<" damage is not equal to "<<data[1].getname()<<endl;
}


void doll::output()
{
cout<<"Name:"<<name<<endl;
cout<<"health->"<<health<<" ammo->"<<ammo<<endl;
cout<<"damage->"<<damage<<" evasion->"<<evasion<<endl<<endl;
}

string doll::getdamage()
{
return damage;
}
string doll::getname()
{
return name;
}
bool equal(doll data1,doll data2)
{
return (data1.getdamage()==data2.getdamage());
}
doll::doll(){
}
doll::doll(string newname,string newhealth,string newammo,string newdamage,string newevasion)
{
name=newname;
health=newhealth;
ammo=newammo;
damage=newdamage;
evasion=newevasion;
}

#include <iostream>
#include <cstdlib>
#include <ctime>
#include <iomanip>

using namespace std;

typedef int* one_star ;
typedef int** double_star ;

int random_array_generator( int rows , int cols )
{
srand( time(NULL) );
double_star result = (double_star)malloc( sizeof(one_star) * rows ) ;

for( int row_index = 0 ; row_index < rows ; row_index++ )
{
result[row_index] = (one_star)malloc( sizeof(int) * cols ) ;
for( int col_index = 0 ; col_index < cols ; col_index++ )
{
result[row_index][col_index] = rand() % 9487 ; //generate random number
}
}

return result ;
}

int main()
{
int rows = 3 , cols = 3;

int **array = random_array_generator( rows , cols );

/* print array*/
for( int row_index = 0 ; row_index < rows ; row_index++ )
{
for( int col_index = 0 ; col_index < cols ; col_index++ )
{
cout << setw(6) << array[row_index][col_index] << " " ;
}
cout << endl ;
}


return EXIT_SUCCESS ;
}

#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

class Doll{
public:
Doll(string newName,int newHealth, int newAmmo,int newDamage,int newEvasion);
Doll();
void output();
string out_name();
int out_health();
int out_ammo();
int out_damage();
int out_evasion();

friend bool equal(Doll data1, Doll data2);

private:
string name;
int health,ammo,damage,evasion;
};

int main(int argc, char** argv) {
Doll data[100];
string instr;
int time=-1;

while(true){
time++;
int dot_time=0;
string n,h,a,d,e,loop;
cout<<"input data as follow format'name,health,ammo,damage,evasion': ";
getline(cin,n,',');
cin>>instr;
for(int i=0;i<instr.length();i++){
if(instr[i] == ',') dot_time++;
//else if(dot_time == 0 ) n += instr[i];
else if(dot_time == 0 ) h += instr[i];
else if(dot_time == 1 ) a += instr[i];
else if(dot_time == 2 ) d += instr[i];
else e += instr[i];
}
if(n[0] == '\n'){
for(int i=0;i<n.length()-1;i++){
n[i]=n[i+1];
}
}
Doll tmp(n,atoi(h.c_str()),atoi(a.c_str()),atoi(d.c_str()),atoi(e.c_str()));
data[time] = tmp;
cout<<"Have nect input data(y/n)? ";
cin>>loop;
if(loop!="y" && loop != "Y") break;
}
cout<<endl;
for(int i=0;i<=time;i++){
data[i].output();
}

if(equal(data[0],data[1]))cout<<"equal!";
else cout<<data[0].out_name()<<" is not equal to "<<data[1].out_name();

return 0;
}

Doll::Doll(string newName,int newHealth, int newAmmo,int newDamage,int newEvasion){
name = newName;
health = newHealth;
ammo = newAmmo;
damage = newDamage;
evasion = newEvasion;
}

Doll::Doll(){
}

void Doll::output(){
cout<<"Name: "<<name<<endl;
cout<<"health->"<<health<<" ammo->"<<ammo<<endl;
cout<<"damage->"<<damage<<" evasion->"<<evasion<<endl<<endl;
}

string Doll::out_name(){
return name;
}

int Doll::out_damage(){
return damage;
}
bool equal(Doll data1, Doll data2){
return(data1.out_damage() == data2.out_damage());
}

#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

long conver(long targ, long ori, long res){
long d2 = 0,i=0;
while(targ>0){
d2 = d2+(targ%res)*pow(ori,i);
cout<<" + "<<(targ%res)<<" * "<<pow(ori,i)<<" = ";
cout<<d2<<endl;
targ/=res;
i++;
}
return d2;
}


int main(){
cout<<conver(13,10,2);
}
